{"tid":1449722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再吹奏啲火魔法同土魔法係内鬼做!","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:36:15.000Z","uid":292125,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2c7d926a9b0e9e2582f24e3faf01d838a3b78376","tid":1449722,"uid":292125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:11.000Z","msg":"今日見到好多人喺網上不斷咁樣講<br />\n話之前嘅火魔法同土魔法 都係內鬼做嘅<br />\n老實講 好多都曲直難分<br />\n但真係唔好再繼續吹奏呢樣嘢<br />\n咁樣同之前話啲前線係鬼嘅人有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n就我個人嚟講 我反而唔介意佢哋喺度做內鬼<br />\n佢哋幫我哋解鎖火魔法不知幾好添<br />\n問題只係佢哋現身嗰陣會拉鳩我哋<br />\n所以要諗辦法點樣處理呢件事<br />\n<br />\n喺facebook上見到呢篇文 互勉之<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2584562688260520&amp;id=972393926144079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2584562688260520%26id%3D972393926144079&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpqjD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=0fe1bd23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2584562688260520&amp;id=972393926144079</a>"},{"pid":"eb370815caae1381ede5da7330ae65fc37ffb5f0","tid":1449722,"uid":296646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d723f676ce65eb9d60c4b1f3c662034b49e91b8","tid":1449722,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"2019年8月11日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449598</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"905101047d9db0ed654714fdf2a4074c054d7f62","tid":1449722,"uid":172596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:25:39.000Z","msg":"Agree<br />\n<br />\n法律上話之前嘅事係黑狗做，亦唔會幫到之前嘅被捕義士"},{"pid":"af77b0ff93a79ad2f9ab352041a833bcdf14f780","tid":1449722,"uid":292125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:36:15.000Z","msg":"自推一次咁多"}]}